{"tid":985711,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒狠批亂關後台程式，Nokia 情況最嚴重","createTime":"2019-01-18T00:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T05:38:30.000Z","uid":23677,"like":29,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c6c58ff5d596d45a073eabc4833eae2ecd886e","tid":985711,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:04:50.000Z","msg":"智能手機續航時間已經成為用戶購買手機的重要標準之一。 Google 為改善電池續航，先後為 Android 系統加入 Doze 和 Adaptive Battery 等功能。而很多廠商卻選擇加入自家的程序，來強制關掉後台運行的軟件。最近，網站 <a href=\"http://DontKillMyApp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDontKillMyApp.com&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=da8222a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">DontKillMyApp.com</a> 就對此批評了部分手機廠商。<br />\n<br />\n據 <a href=\"http://DontKillMyApp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDontKillMyApp.com&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=da8222a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">DontKillMyApp.com</a> 報導，手機廠商將後台運行的軟件強制關閉，可能有助電池的耐用度，但對用戶和開發者來說都未必是好事。強制關閉程序，可能會導致軟件無法達到預期效果，容易引起用戶對開發者們的誤解。本次，網站對幾大知名手機廠商進行評分，其中 Nokia 在 Android O 和 Android P 中加入「電池保護」程序，當用戶將手機屏幕關閉，程序在20分鐘後就會將所有後台運行的軟件強制關閉。這個做法令用戶部分軟件會有影響，其中包括安裝的第三方鬧鐘。所以，Nokia 評分最差獲得「五舊屎」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，OnePlus 倒數第二獲「四舊屎」；小米、華為、魅族和 Sony 也存在這種行為，並列倒數第三。對系統原生態保護較好的有，Samsung 、 HTC 和原生 Android 系統。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/18/080431_2567655b8ff9a3bfec5ae6ebc6ec077f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F18%2F080431_2567655b8ff9a3bfec5ae6ebc6ec077f.jpg&h=c99c9dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/01/17/smartphones-are-turning-back-into-dumbphones/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F01%2F17%2Fsmartphones-are-turning-back-into-dumbphones%2F&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=97b87b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/01/17/smartphones-are-turning-back-into-dumbphones/</a>"},{"pid":"a445ac194de5cd72b08bac45c273027da9eeee63","tid":985711,"uid":216800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:07:45.000Z","msg":"屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639c1427303cc75b753362720b4c8a979e9b8a7b","tid":985711,"uid":158301,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"同連登仔唱反調"},{"pid":"fec8b7eb215b522da825e1cc43bc66e3f721e6eb","tid":985711,"uid":609,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"Android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1e70a112af41d1ed7da00341e179e7f89b3c80","tid":985711,"uid":78399,"like":10,"dislike":17,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:13:11.000Z","msg":"熄mon 廿分鐘後先關都好合理"},{"pid":"4e040d87224a00ca7756cda6570ee862dc63b305","tid":985711,"uid":51932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:14:02.000Z","msg":"真多工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1f49520e8606588930d9e565dec28267325d29","tid":985711,"uid":191815,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"原生都食一舊屎<br />\n即係無一間值得用？"},{"pid":"3e66894b875b86a1213c186f5d06dcf5049ec332","tid":985711,"uid":23677,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"7b1f49520e8606588930d9e565dec28267325d29","tid":985711,"uid":191815,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"原生都食一舊屎<br />\n即係無一間值得用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:18:03.000Z","msg":"冇屎唔係代表完全唔kill app咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c375f7a64c06c4b2e4a22b6a2e58d8a8963e70ce","tid":985711,"uid":104804,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,