ick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40fa97abd0e4d5223153b54e4be35ee5b97872e","tid":985711,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"之前換咗8.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8e946c1a87d3b1788b5ac8e92044c617bdc114","tid":985711,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"Nokia Android 9, 自動調節亮度 點用好？<br />\n<br />\n係夜晚全黑時，佢唔調去最暗，會調光少少。我覺得過亮。我要變為 人手調節，手動校去最暗。<br />\n<br />\n我想佢個 自動調節，會係全黑環境，調去最暗mon ，有冇得搞？"},{"pid":"cac299feed165368478f3287c86daec31643413e","tid":985711,"uid":87600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e9d2fd3ac68d0f3efb30982df1f339486a7d91","tid":985711,"uid":12599,"like":11,"dislike":13,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:24:51.000Z","msg":"appled機仲嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"有無資料support<br />\n否則就係尻up"},{"pid":"6e40fe72f86d6d67df5ee2034f27942a86f840ea","tid":985711,"uid":25971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9c6c58ff5d596d45a073eabc4833eae2ecd886e","tid":985711,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:04:50.000Z","msg":"智能手機續航時間已經成為用戶購買手機的重要標準之一。 Google 為改善電池續航，先後為 Android 系統加入 Doze 和 Adaptive Battery 等功能。而很多廠商卻選擇加入自家的程序，來強制關掉後台運行的軟件。最近，網站 <a href=\"http://DontKillMyApp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDontKillMyApp.com&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=da8222a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">DontKillMyApp.com</a> 就對此批評了部分手機廠商。<br />\n<br />\n據 <a href=\"http://DontKillMyApp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDontKillMyApp.com&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=da8222a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">DontKillMyApp.com</a> 報導，手機廠商將後台運行的軟件強制關閉，可能有助電池的耐用度，但對用戶和開發者來說都未必是好事。強制關閉程序，可能會導致軟件無法達到預期效果，容易引起用戶對開發者們的誤解。本次，網站對幾大知名手機廠商進行評分，其中 Nokia 在 Android O 和 Android P 中加入「電池保護」程序，當用戶將手機屏幕關閉，程序在20分鐘後就會將所有後台運行的軟件強制關閉。這個做法令用戶部分軟件會有影響，其中包括安裝的第三方鬧鐘。所以，Nokia 評分最差獲得「五舊屎」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，OnePlus 倒數第二獲「四舊屎」；小米、華為、魅族和 Sony 也存在這種行為，並列倒數第三。對系統原生態保護較好的有，Samsung 、 HTC 和原生 Android 系統。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/18/080431_2567655b8ff9a3bfec5ae6ebc6ec077f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F18%2F080431_2567655b8ff9a3bfec5ae6ebc6ec077f.jpg&h=c99c9dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/01/17/smartphones-are-turning-back-into-dumbphones/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F01%2F17%2Fsmartphones-are-turning-back-into-dumbphones%2F&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=97b87b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/01/17/smartphones-are-turning-back-into-dumbphones/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"有HTC反而冇LG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}